So we first started this video tutorial by showing you how to enable the water plugin.

3
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Remember, once you've enabled it, you do need to restart the editor.

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
We then showed you how to set up a world.

5
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Remember the water tools, no matter which one you're using, does require a landscape in order to work.

6
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.000
So make sure your worlds do contain that so that you can utilize those tools and your projects.

7
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:36.000
