8
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.000
their controls on them are actually very similar.

9
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:46.000
We then took a look at how we combined the river, lakes and ocean tools together in a single map to give us a landscape

10
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
that's got a lake with a river that goes into the ocean.

11
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:56.000
And then we finished with covering waves and buoyancy.

12
00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Remember waves can be stored to an asset to allow us to take this very complicated, but very powerful tool into an easy to use asset

13
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
that we can share between our rivers, lakes and oceans.

14
00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.000
